www.malonebailey.com We’re One of the Big Guys, But We Don’t Act Like It Founded in 1982, MaloneBailey is a full-service public accounting firm headquartered in Houston and with offices in Beijing and Shenzhen. MaloneBailey provides audit, tax and consulting services to public and private companies from a variety of industry lines.

We are proud to offer a unique value proposition that revolves around three key areas: Service, Competence and Fees. Service: We practice a hands-on, service-oriented business with a focus on quality, reliability, and responsiveness to our clients’ needs. Partner involvement at all stages of the engagement is key to our process and we’re effective in serving our clients because we’re passionate about what we do. We anticipate our clients’ needs and frequent deadlines and work within those parameters to always be there for our clients.

Competence: Our service offering includes audit, tax and consulting services for both public and private companies in a variety of industry lines. For our clients, this translates into a depth of experience characterized by an enduring commitment to the delivery of quality and efficiency in all that we do with methodologies designed for audit specialization.

Fees: We deliver large-firm quality audits efficiently without charging large firm fees. We have developed methodologies for delivering competent and efficient audits. In other words, we have the technical expertise to understand the accounting and reporting issues while maintaining a cost competitive fee structure. With unequivocal respect for our clients’ finances, we strive to be efficient, cost effective and transparent with the delivery of our services and professional fees.
